title: (Fri Full) Luke Combs on Finding Out He Was Going To Be A Dad, The Unusual Place He Met Up with Ed Sheeran and Details On Upcoming Album +   Amy Got Bit by a Tick & She’s Worried About Lyme Disease
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Luke Combs on Finding Out He Was Going To Be A Dad, The Unusual Place He Met Up with Ed Sheeran and Details On Upcoming Album +   Amy Got Bit by a Tick & She’s Worried About Lyme Disease
description:
Luke Combs stops by the studio to talk about his upcoming album, where he found out he was becoming a dad, and the unusual place he met up with Ed Sheeran.  Amy is worried after getting bit by a tick recently. We get an update from Lunchbox’s Uber charges that he thinks were caused by the Haunted Doll.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
